div.font:
Raft Log
Persist transfer requests unconditionally, even if it is a
duplicated one.
In real life, one raft log entry may consist of a batch of
transfer requests to amortize the fsync cost.

div.font:
Event Log
The balance change event generated by the transfer
request.
Each event is assigned a consecutive integer starting
from 1, which is used by downstream systems to verify
the integrity of the event stream.
N.B., a duplicated transfer request in raft log will be
detected by DedupId Store and discarded, leaving the
BalanceMap unchanged and no event generated.
